## Required Actions for Wix + Vercel Integration
-------------------------------------------------

### Step 1: Verify/Setup Vercel Deployment
1. Go to vercel.com and sign in
2. Import the GitHub repository (yelush19/Panda_Payroll)
3. Set output directory to "docs"
4. Deploy and get the deployment URL (e.g., panda-payroll.vercel.app)

### Step 2: Configure Wix DNS for Subdomain
1. Go to Wix Dashboard > Domains
2. Select your domain
3. Go to DNS Settings
4. Add CNAME record:
   - Name: payroll (or desired subdomain)
   - Value: cname.vercel-dns.com
5. Wait for DNS propagation (up to 48 hours)

### Step 3: Configure Custom Domain in Vercel
1. Go to Vercel project settings > Domains
2. Add custom domain: payroll.yourdomain.com
3. Vercel will verify DNS configuration
4. Enable SSL certificate (automatic)

